trans-unit.source: Pure Python implementation of ASN.1 and Z39.50 v3,
Z39.50 (ZOOM API), ASN.1, and MARC implementations
with a simple MARC parser thrown in. See the URL for details. This is a fork of Aaron Lav’s original PyZ3950, now maintained by the Mobile Oxford team at Oxford University Computing Services
trans-unit.target: 并附带一个简单的MARC解析器。有关详细信息，请参见URL。这是亚伦·拉夫（Aaron Lav）最初的PyZ3950的叉子，现在由牛津大学计算服务部的移动牛津团队维护。
